# b4_ceiling.shot — sustained jet to the world's y=0 boundary.
#
# fuel_max is 1.0 s; full-throttle jet for 100 ticks rises ~1500 px,
# more than the world height (1280 px) so the player crashes into the
# top boundary. We capture the climb tick-by-tick around the ceiling
# impact so we can see whether out-of-bounds-as-solid mangles the
# constraint solver.

window 1280 720
seed   1 1
out    build/shots/b4
mouse  900 360
contact_sheet sheet cols 4 cell 480 270

at  10 shot stand_t010

at  30 press jet
burst climb from 50 to 130 every 10
at 130 release jet

burst fall from 140 to 240 every 15

at 280 end
